title: All of Kate McKinnon's Amazing Political Impressions on 'SNL'
text:
All of Kate McKinnon's Amazing Political Impressions on 'SNL' 
She's crushed impressions of everyone from Hillary Clinton to Jeff Sessions. view gallery 06 Photos 
Kate McKinnon has been crushing it on Saturday Night Live lately, thanks in no small part to her spot-on political impersonations. Her Hillary Clinton will go down as an iconic SNL impression, but her appearances as everyone from Kellyanne Conway to Jeff Sessions have also been incredible. Here are some of Kate's best political impersonations. More
